## Summary

Created **`apps/web/src/features/studyPlan/storage/studyPlanStore.ts`** â€” an IndexedDB storage module using Dexie, with Zod schema validation.

### Two object stores

| Store | Key | Description |
|-------|-----|-------------|
| `studyPlans` | `id` | Full plan entries (`StudyPlanStoreEntry`) with versioning |
| `dailyPlans` | `id` | Individual day items (`DailyPlanItem`) with compound indexes on `planId+date`, `planId+dayNumber`, `planId+phaseName`, `planId+status` |

### CRUD APIs

- `savePlan`, `getPlan`, `getAllPlans`, `deletePlan`, `planExists`
- `saveGlobalStrategy`, `getGlobalStrategy`
- `saveDailyPlan`, `saveDailyPlans`, `getDailyPlans`, `getDailyPlan`, `getDailyPlanByDayNumber`
- `updateDailyPlanStatus`, `updateDailyPlan`, `deleteDailyPlan`
- `updatePlanMeta`, `saveProfileAndMeta`
- `deleteDailyPlans`, `clearAll`

### Missing/invalid day query APIs

- `getGeneratedDayNumbers(planId)` â€” returns `Set<number>` of day numbers that exist
- `getMissingDayNumbers(planId, expectedDayNumbers)` â€” finds which days are missing
- `getDaysInDateRange(planId, startDate, endDate)` â€” filter by date range
- `getDaysByWeek(planId, weekNumber)` â€” filter by week
- `getDaysByPhase(planId, phaseName)` â€” filter by phase
- `getDaysByStatus(planId, status)` â€” filter by completion status
- `getIncompleteDays(planId)` â€” returns not-started/in-progress/partially-complete days
- `getDaysCountByStatus(planId)` â€” returns status distribution counts
- `getGenerationProgress(planId)` â€” returns `{generatedDays, totalDays, percentage}`

### Design

- Stable IDs via `crypto.randomUUID()`
- `createdAt`/`updatedAt` timestamps on every entity (preserved across updates)
- `DailyPlanItem` status field with 5 states: `not-started`, `in-progress`, `completed`, `skipped`, `partially-completed`
- All writes validated with Zod schemas before storage
- Singleton `StudyPlanDexie` instance with `getDb()`/`destroyDb()` lifecycle
